      "text": "角が立つと面倒ですから",
      "startTime": 76.7662359556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ryokan-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ryokan-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.8995692889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうですね、ラスベガスでライブをした時は",
      "startTime": 78.8995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mhk-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "お世話になりました",
      "startTime": 82.5995692889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "海外公演は久々でしたし、いい経験になりました",
